RequestDispatcher
It is an interface available in javax.servlet package.
It has below methods:-
a)forward()
If you want to forward the request(HttpServerRequest) from servet to html/jsp/servlet

b)include()
If you want to include some resources(html/jsp/servlet) then use include()

Diff b/n forward() & include()
forward() method:you can place many forward() methods in 1 servlet conditionaly to forward the control but only 1 
forward() will be executed.

include() method:you can place many include() methods in a servlet and all include() methods will be executed.
 
NOTE:You can restrict the user from accesing the resource(html/jsp) by placing the page under WEB-INF folder/directory